{"tid":1766115,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［重貼］［大伏］記住咪撚申請港澳居住證，申請咗就要交社保","createTime":"2019-12-02T10:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T10:41:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6b2e97f1eadf8452ff09463dea2ef000686a4772","tid":1766115,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T10:41:31.000Z","msg":"&quot;第12條：<strong>港澳台居民居住證持有人在居住地依法<ins>享受勞動就業，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">參加社會保險，繳存</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">、提取和使用住房公積金的權利。</span></ins></strong> <br />\n<br />\n用&quot;享受&quot;, &quot;權利&quot;黎描述參加社保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔見有取消方法, 只有官方同你作癈方法, i.e.好可能non-reversible<br />\n<br />\n&quot;第15條：港澳台居民居住證持證人有下列情形之一的，其所持居住證應當由簽發機關宣布作廢：<br />\n<br />\n喪失港澳台居民身份的；<br />\n使用虛假證明材料騙領港澳台居民居住證的；<br />\n可能對國家主權、安全、榮譽和利益造成危害的；<br />\n港澳台居民出入境證件被註銷、收繳或者宣布作廢的（正常換補發情形除外）。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論:雖然傳話有五年豁免<br />\n5年後, 好可能一係交社保, 一係移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2141353/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%85%E4%BD%8F%E8%AD%89%E7%94%B3%E9%A0%98%E7%99%BC%E6%94%BE%E8%BE%A6%E6%B3%95%20%E5%85%A8%E6%96%87%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2141353%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25B1%2585%25E4%25BD%258F%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%2594%25B3%25E9%25A0%2598%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E6%25B3%2595%2520%25E5%2585%25A8%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%25B8%2583&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRQTszQqcSrFeuHGFn5Djw6E%3D&h=f3ca2a96\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2141353/%E6%B8%AF%E6%BE%B3%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E5%B1%85%E4%B